#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "E-mail address"</h2>
To use this software, you must provide your e-mail address when you create
your account.  On creation, or if you change your e-mail in the administration
menu, e-mail will be sent to this address with confirmation instructions.
<p>Some functions will not work without confirmed e-mail.
